Hello there -

This is the daily report for <%= @date.to_s(:db) %>.

The following <%= @todays_users.size %> users signed up today:
<% @todays_users.each do |u| -%>
<%= u.realname -%> (<%= u.user_name -%>, <%= u.email -%>)
<% end -%>

The following <%= @todays_groups.size %> projects were created today:
<% @todays_groups.each do |g| %>
<%= g.unix_group_name -%> (<%= truncate(g.short_description, 80) -%>) which is owned by <%= g.first_admin.user_name -%>
<% end %>

The following <%= @todays_forum_messages.size %> forum messages were posted today:
<% @todays_forum_messages.each do |m| %>
<%= m.posted_by.user_name -%> (<%= m.posted_by.user_id -%>) posted on <%= m.forum_group.group.unix_group_name -%>: <%= truncate(m.subject, 40) -%>
<% end %>

The following <%= @todays_opened_artifacts.size %> new artifacts were opened today:
<% @todays_opened_artifacts.each do |a| %>
<%= a.submitted_by.user_name -%> (<%= a.submitted_by.user_id -%>) posted to <%= a.artifact_group_list.group.unix_group_name %>: <%= truncate(a.summary,50) -%>
<% end %>

The following <%= @todays_released_files.size %> files were released today:
<% @todays_released_files.each do |f| %>
<%= f.release.package.group.unix_group_name -%> released <%= f.filename -%>
<% end %>

